headline: Confluent (NASDAQ:CFLT) Exceeds Q4 CY2025 Expectations But Large Customer Wins Slow Down
summary: Data streaming platform provider Confluent (NASDAQ:CFLT) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q4 CY2025, with sales up 20.5% year on year to $314.8 million. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.12 per share was 21.1% above analysts’ consensus estimates.

headline: IBM AI FlashSystem And QRadar Updates Shape Storage And Security Story
summary: IBM (NYSE:IBM) introduced its next-generation AI-powered FlashSystem storage platform, described as the company's most significant upgrade in six years. The new FlashSystem features AI-driven autonomous storage with built-in efficiency, security, and ransomware detection capabilities. IBM also expanded its security portfolio through integrations between QRadar security platforms and the Criminal IP threat intelligence solution.
